# Podcasts
CUAppDev's podcast app API documentation

# Group Users
## Google Sign In [/api/v1/users/google_sign_in?id_token={id_token}]
### Google Sign In [POST]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "data": {
            "user": {
              "email": "john.doe@gmail.com",
              "firstName": "John",
              "googleId": "12345",
              "id": "8361c722-0513-11e7-9fc2-7b1dcc97b110",
              "imageUrl": "https://goo.gl/L37gfS",
              "lastName": "Doe",
              "numberFollowers": 0,
              "numberFollowing": 0,
              "session": {
                "expiresAt": 1489636800000,
                "sessionToken": "myLongSessionToken",
                "type": "session",
                "updateToken": "myLongUpdateToken"
              },
              "type": "user",
              "username": "johndoe"
            },
            "newUser": true
          },
          "success": true
        }


