# Group Subscriptions
## Subscriptions CRUD [/api/v1/subscriptions?series_id={id}]
### Create Subscription [POST]

+ Request

  + Headers

            Authorization : Bearer {sessionToken}

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "data": {
            "subscription": {
              "userId": 123,
              "seriesId": 456,
              "username": "abc",
              "userImageUrl": "image1.jpg",
              "userFirstName": "name",
              "userLastName": "name",
              "seriesTitle": "title",
              "seriesImageUrlSm": "image2.jpg"
            }
          },
          "success": true
        }

